OL,3,CDrainage pump 'deliberately sabotaged'
OL,4,Cto flood rail line
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after a
OL,7,Fdrainage pump was deliberately
OL,8,Fsabotaged in a "senseless act of
OL,9,Fvandalism" causing a rail line to
OL,10,Fflood in severe weather.
OL,12,FTrains between Chester and Hooton were
OL,13,Funable to run after the pump's wires
OL,14,Fwere cut in Ellesmere Port, Cheshire,
OL,15,Fintentionally destroying it ahead of
OL,16,Fforecast heavy rain.
