OL,3,CDrainage pump 'deliberately sabotaged'
OL,4,Cto flood rail line
OL,6,FNetwork Rail said it was impossible to
OL,7,Frepair the damage to the control panel
OL,8,Fof the two-tonne machine on site, and
OL,9,Fengineers will now have to install a
OL,10,Fnew pump, costing the taxpayer an
OL,11,Festimated #30,000.
OL,13,FThe pump is essential to the drainage
OL,14,Fof the track in the area, which is
OL,15,Fsusceptible to flooding and is now
OL,16,Fcompletely submerged in places.
OL,18,FBritish Transport Police is now
OL,19,Finvestigating the incident.
