OL,3,CDrainage pump 'deliberately sabotaged'
OL,4,Cto flood rail line
OL,6,FPhil James, Network Rail's North West
OL,7,Froute director, said: "I am disgusted
OL,8,Fby this senseless act of vandalism,
OL,9,Fwhich has caused rail disruption for
OL,10,Four passengers, and increased the busy
OL,11,Fworkload of our frontline teams during
OL,12,Fa period of very heavy rainfall.
OL,14,F"We are working to install a new
OL,15,Fdrainage pump as soon as possible to
OL,16,Fclear the water and get passengers on
OL,17,Fthe move between Chester and Hooton
OL,18,Fagain.
