OL,6,F"A report has been made to the British
OL,7,FTransport Police who are investigating
OL,8,Fthis criminal act."
OL,10,FA new pump is being delivered and
OL,11,Finstalled, and once it is up and
OL,12,Frunning, engineers expect the flooding
OL,13,Fto recede.
OL,15,FFollowing inspections and any further
OL,16,Frepairs needed to the railway, the
OL,17,Fline will reopen between Chester and
OL,18,FHooton.
